headline: Watching the Narrative for FICO Shift After New Mortgage Program and Analyst Reactions
summary: Fair Isaac's stock outlook has been refreshed, with the Fair Value Estimate now raised from $1,913 to $2,017 following an improved view of the company's prospects. This change comes as the discounted rate has eased slightly, and future revenue growth projections have been upgraded. The outlook reflects optimism around new business initiatives and ongoing industry leadership. Stay tuned to discover how investors can keep pace with the fast-evolving narrative surrounding Fair Isaac's growth...
